Repeat: sl 1 wyib, k1, (k1, yo, k1, yo, k1) in next stitch, k1
sl 1 wyif, k1, k5 wrapping yarn twice for each stitch, k1
sl 5 wyib dropping extra wraps, k3
insert needle into first 3 stitches as if to k3 tog, and slip the stitches from this position; k2-tog, then pass the 3 slipped stitches all together over the k2-tog stitch, k3
(k1, yo, k1, yo, k1) in next stitch, k1, sl 1 wyib, k1

insert needle into first 3 stitches as if to k3 tog, and slip the stitches from this position; k2-tog, then pass the 3 slipped stitches all together over the k2-tog stitch, k3
